{
  "video_id": "KpH4Zo9cATM",
  "title": "How Do Trees Know When It's Spring?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 5960.0,
      "end_time": 6960.0,
      "text": "Hey, I&#39;m Rob."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 7600.0,
      "end_time": 9360.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d wondered for a long time how trees"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 9360.0,
      "end_time": 11200.0,
      "text": "sensed it was spring and knew to bloom."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 11780.0,
      "end_time": 13680.0,
      "text": "We went to the National Arboretum here in D.C."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13680.0,
      "end_time": 14580.0,
      "text": "to find out."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24300.0,
      "end_time": 26140.0,
      "text": "You could sort of think of spring as"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26140.0,
      "end_time": 27380.0,
      "text": "adolescence for a tree."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28880.0,
      "end_time": 30480.0,
      "text": "For us, that&#39;s not always fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 30480.0,
      "end_time": 32400.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s sort of the same thing for a tree."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32400.0,
      "end_time": 33000.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a huge change."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 33560.0,
      "end_time": 35800.0,
      "text": "When you look at a dormant tree"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 35800.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "and what that looks like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 36760.0,
      "end_time": 39300.0,
      "text": "and what it looks like when it&#39;s in flower, and everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40200.0,
      "end_time": 41720.0,
      "text": "those are way different-looking things."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 41720.0,
      "end_time": 43339.0,
      "text": "If you were from another planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 44320.0,
      "end_time": 45600.0,
      "text": "you might look at that, and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45600.0,
      "end_time": 47100.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s not the same organism."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 48180.0,
      "end_time": 48940.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m Scott Aker."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 48940.0,
      "end_time": 51199.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m the head of horticulture and education"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 51200.0,
      "end_time": 52920.0,
      "text": "here at the U.S. National Arboretum."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 53680.0,
      "end_time": 55960.0,
      "text": "We have a scientific mission primarily here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 56460.0,
      "end_time": 57800.0,
      "text": "but we are also a public garden."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 62200.0,
      "end_time": 67800.0,
      "text": "How do trees know to bloom in the spring?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68300.0,
      "end_time": 69399.0,
      "text": "How do they know it&#39;s time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 69400.0,
      "end_time": 72140.0,
      "text": "Actually, it has more to do with the length"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72140.0,
      "end_time": 74580.0,
      "text": "of the nighttime than it does with temperature."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 74580.0,
      "end_time": 76700.0,
      "text": "Most people think that it gets warmer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 76700.0,
      "end_time": 78420.0,
      "text": "and we all learned this in grade school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78420.0,
      "end_time": 81240.0,
      "text": "it gets warmer, and the buds start coming on the trees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 81240.0,
      "end_time": 82220.0,
      "text": "and then they bloom."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 82580.0,
      "end_time": 84500.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually not as simple as that."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 84500.0,
      "end_time": 87560.0,
      "text": "Plants have a funky little molecule in them"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 87560.0,
      "end_time": 88720.0,
      "text": "called phytochrome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 89160.0,
      "end_time": 90440.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s like an hourglass."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 91920.0,
      "end_time": 94320.0,
      "text": "The hourglass, or the molecules, is flipped"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 96980.0,
      "text": "very soon after the sun goes down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 97620.0,
      "end_time": 99620.0,
      "text": "and then you think of time that it takes"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 99620.0,
      "end_time": 101480.0,
      "text": "the grains of sand to go through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101760.0,
      "end_time": 104400.0,
      "text": "if there&#39;s enough time that"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 104980.0,
      "end_time": 106760.0,
      "text": "the whole hourglass empties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 108400.0,
      "end_time": 111780.0,
      "text": "the plant gets the idea that we should hold off."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 111780.0,
      "end_time": 113300.0,
      "text": "The nights are still pretty long."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 113740.0,
      "end_time": 115500.0,
      "text": "But then you have that one magical night that"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 115500.0,
      "end_time": 118600.0,
      "text": "not all the phytochrome is changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 118620.0,
      "end_time": 120540.0,
      "text": "The bud gets a signal that it&#39;s time to get going,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 121560.0,
      "end_time": 123580.0,
      "text": "and then we have a period of warmer temperatures"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 123580.0,
      "end_time": 125800.0,
      "text": "that help that development happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126400.0,
      "end_time": 127540.0,
      "text": "If you suddenly get cold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 127860.0,
      "end_time": 130919.0,
      "text": "those buds will get the signal to hang way back"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 130919.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132899.0,
      "text": "if we have one night of drastic cold."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133520.0,
      "end_time": 137140.0,
      "text": "What&#39;re signs that people can look for to say:"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 137140.0,
      "end_time": 138440.0,
      "text": "Oh, this tree is about to bloom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 138680.0,
      "end_time": 140620.0,
      "text": "or this tree is blooming."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 140620.0,
      "end_time": 141960.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s what&#39;s going to come next."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 142280.0,
      "end_time": 145200.0,
      "text": "Of course, the obvious thing is bud swell."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 145280.0,
      "end_time": 147520.0,
      "text": "From a distance, you can see if something looks"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 147520.0,
      "end_time": 148920.0,
      "text": "thick and they&#39;re darker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 149140.0,
      "end_time": 151179.0,
      "text": "if you look closely, you&#39;ll see the little stamens"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 151180.0,
      "end_time": 152920.0,
      "text": "with the pollen on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 153640.0,
      "end_time": 155640.0,
      "text": "Most plants have two different kinds of buds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 155640.0,
      "end_time": 158459.0,
      "text": "and you can see that very clearly this time of year."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 158780.0,
      "end_time": 161200.0,
      "text": "You have big, fat ones that are flower buds."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 161200.0,
      "end_time": 162500.0,
      "text": "They exist to reproduce."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 162500.0,
      "end_time": 164580.0,
      "text": "And then, very often you have closer to the tip,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 164580.0,
      "end_time": 167880.0,
      "text": "skinny, kind of slender ones that are vegetative buds"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 167880.0,
      "end_time": 169220.0,
      "text": "that will produce the growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 170200.0,
      "end_time": 171940.0,
      "text": "The purpose of a tree blooming is one thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 171940.0,
      "end_time": 173160.0,
      "text": "and one thing only,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 173160.0,
      "end_time": 174220.0,
      "text": "and that is reproduction."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 174720.0,
      "end_time": 177140.0,
      "text": "You can see it sometimes if a tree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 177440.0,
      "end_time": 179380.0,
      "text": "if we injured the lot of the root system on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 179380.0,
      "end_time": 180190.0,
      "text": "or something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 180360.0,
      "end_time": 182360.0,
      "text": "it will bloom extra heavily,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 182360.0,
      "end_time": 185360.0,
      "text": "and people will misinterpret that as health."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 186200.0,
      "end_time": 188800.0,
      "text": "Actually, that&#39;s a: I know I&#39;m going to die!"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 189520.0,
      "end_time": 191640.0,
      "text": "But before I die, I want to have lots of kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 192180.0,
      "end_time": 193940.0,
      "text": "and perpetuate my line."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 194360.0,
      "end_time": 196780.0,
      "text": "Trees are beautifully adapted."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 196780.0,
      "end_time": 198640.0,
      "text": "I mean, even if you look at them structurally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 198640.0,
      "end_time": 199700.0,
      "text": "how they&#39;re put together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 200380.0,
      "end_time": 202680.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re more exquisitely, and strongly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 203240.0,
      "end_time": 204980.0,
      "text": "and efficiently built than any of our buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 204980.0,
      "end_time": 206980.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re a tree, you can&#39;t move some place better"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 206980.0,
      "end_time": 208600.0,
      "text": "if conditions get bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 208960.0,
      "end_time": 210280.0,
      "text": "so you have to adapt."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 210920.0,
      "end_time": 213799.0,
      "text": "I guess I&#39;m always really surprised at how"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 213800.0,
      "end_time": 215600.0,
      "text": "adaptable trees are."
    }
  ]
}